@arne_hou_uerkflinch 's offset wayfair has been on a bit of a back burner these past few months, but I've been back at it this last week, I'm now in the slow process of building up layers of oil for the finish.

I really love the body shape on this build, Arne designed the F hole, and had good feel for the idea of the lines, but gave me more or less complete creative freedom to  do what I want with it, and I think it came out great!

Plan on having it done in around a month.
